bable situations</strong>. Team coordination and communication are key to maintaining order and controlling the madness of this place, but remember, the customer is always right (even lazy sloths and candy-loving gummy bears)!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Book your room for an individual experience or bring your friends to enjoy team action.</strong> Up to 4 players can immerse themselves in this world full of challenges and laughter, where the better the cooperation, the cleaner the rooms, and the happier the hosted customers. Do you like games that appeal to both children and adults alike? Look no further, because <i><strong>Welcome to Empyreum</strong></i> is the ultimate choice for experiencing unparalleled moments with your loved ones!</p>","developers":["Tapioca Games"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807220/header.jpg?t=1727008618","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"Welcome to Empyreum \u00a9 2024 Developed and published by Tapioca Games. All other trademarks, logos and copyrights are property of their respective owners. All rights reserved.","linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256858196,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256858196/movie480.mp4?t=1710016413","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256858196/movie_max.mp4?t=1710016413"},"name":"Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256858196/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1710016413","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256858196/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1710016413","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256858196/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1710016413"}}],"name":"Welcome to Empyreum","package_groups":[{"descrip